These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cauliflower, zucchini, carrot, lettuce, pineapple, apricot, plum
1. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
3. the person eating carrot is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person eating plum##7
4. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |  7   |
| Food   | pineapple | apricot | carrot | plum | cauliflower | zucchini | lettuce |

