.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-2::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, poker, canasta, snooker, chess, billiard, backgammon
 1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 2. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing poker##7
 3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 4. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 5. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the person playing chess##7
 6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 8. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 9. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
10. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3     |    4    |      5      |     6      |   7    |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta | chess | poker | billiard | snooker | scrabble |

