.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, skydiving, camping, drawing, singing, writing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is singing##7
2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is writing##7
7. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1  |   2   |   3    |   4   |     5      |  6  |     7      |
| Hobby   | board-games | writing | camping | singing | skydiving | hiking | drawing |

