.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, badminton, weightlifting, rowing, lacrosse, cycling, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
4. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is cycling##2
6. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is cricket##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |    7    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | cricket | skiing | cycling | lacrosse | badminton | rowing |

