 5. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 6. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsdaisy##7
10. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |   3   |  4  |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Flower   | iris | balloon-flower | zinnia | begonia | daisy | poppy | bellflower |

