2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |      3      |      4       |     5     |    6    |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | crime | thriller | martial-arts | epic | spy | documentary |

