.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-7::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: december, august, january, september, february, march, may
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in march##7
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
5. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in january##2
6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
7. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
8. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Birthday   | september | august | may | january | march | december | february |

