 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the ferret##7
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the hedgehog##7
 6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 7. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
10. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1        |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5        |      6      |     7     |
| Pet   | goat | hedgehog | mouse | guinea-pig | chinchilla | turtle | ferret |

